# Caddy provisions and renews a Let's Encrypt certificate for the host below on
# its own, as long as the DNS A record points at this VPS and ports 80 and 443
# are reachable. It terminates TLS and reverse-proxies to the relayer daemon,
# which listens on localhost only (never expose 4663 to the public internet).

relay.cowlprotocol.com {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:4663
}
